text: Woluwe-Saint-Lambert (in French) or Sint-Lambrechts-Woluwe (in Dutch) is a municipality in Belgium, in the Brussels-Capital Region. In 2007, 48315 people lived there. It is at 50° 51 North, 04° 25 East. == References == Category:Municipalities of Brussels-Capital Region
title: Woluwe-Saint-Lambert
